<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>IcePlant Management Portal</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f7f9;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #0e75b9;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        .subtitle {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        .loading {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .feature-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .feature-item {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            width: 250px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .feature-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .feature-item h3 {
            color: #0e75b9;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>IcePlant Management Portal</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">Efficient Ice Plant Operations Management</div>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="loading">
            <p>Loading application...</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-list">
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>Time and Attendance</h3>
                <p>Track employee check-ins, calculate working hours, and manage department assignments.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>Sales Management</h3>
                <p>Record ice block sales, track buyer information, and manage payment methods.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>Inventory Management</h3>
                <p>Monitor ice block stock levels, track raw materials, and receive low stock alerts.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>Expense Tracking</h3>
                <p>Record expenses, categorize them, and generate comprehensive expense reports.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 